Package: geopr
Title: Access Puerto Rico GeoServer WFS Layers
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lanselotte", "Oliveras Vega", , "lanselotte.oliveras@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides helper functions to list and download geospatial layers
    from the Puerto Rico government GeoServer WFS endpoint. Layers are returned
    as sf objects ready for analysis and mapping. Includes tools for interactive
    preview and saving layers in multiple geospatial formats.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
